data.description: Welcome to 15903 Hollow Rock Drive! This beautifuly remodeled home sits on a large corner lot.  As you enter you are greeted by beautiful wide plank luxury vinyl flooring throughout the home. The dining room is on your right and leads to a large kitchen which is open to the den with a gas log fireplace. Sunny breakfast room allows views of the large backyard. Plenty of room for kids and pets!  The back patio is spacious and provides shade and weather protection with a covered pergola.  The primary suite is spacious and primary bathroom has been completely remodeled with a new double vanity, quartz counter tops. designer lighting and fixtures.  Upstairs you will find a huge gameroom and three spacious bedrooms which share a full bathroom. The home has been recently painted inside and out. HVAC is approximately 3 years old. New stainless-steel range in kitchen.  Highly acclaimed Klein ISD. Located near excellent shopping and restaurants in the Vintage area. Come see this beauty today!!
